entries.title: WATCH:  Elephant seal interrupts business on Australia pier
entries.description: A large elephant seal in Australia is causing a stir, closing off a pier to locals, tourists and preventing a dog owner from taking her dogs on their usual walking path.

entries.title: Donald Trump allowed back on Facebook and Instagram, Meta announces

entries.title: Charge dropped against Afghan soldier seeking asylum in US

entries.title: Panic! at the Disco ends; Brendon Urie to focus on family

entries.title: Member of Congress reads AI-generated speech on House floor

entries.title: Arrest made after Microsoft executive, father of 4 gunned down in 'targeted ambush'

entries.title: Teacher shot by 6-year-old says school was warned 4 times, announces lawsuit

entries.title: Drug company and doctor sue over abortion pill access, in test case of federal power

entries.title: Lloyd Morrisett, who helped launch 'Sesame Street,' dies

entries.title: 2 charged by DOJ for targeting anti-abortion clinics in Florida

entries.title: Texas senator proposes laws allowing school shooting victims to sue state

entries.title: Howard University given $90 million for military research in Pentagon partnership
